dc_title_s: Fire Department Response Districts Jackson County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data layer represents Fire Department response districts in Jackson County, Wisconsin in 2020. [This digital geospatial dataset is a current representation of all Fire Response Zones in Jackson County, Wisconsin, with attributes standardized in accordance to the NENA Standard for NG9-1-1 GIS Data Model (NENA-STA-006.1-2018). Responding fire departments include Alma Center Fire Department, Augusta Department of Natural Resources, Black River Falls Fire Department, Black River Falls Department of Natural Resources, City Point Fire Department, Fairchild Fire Department, Farmington Fire Department, Hatfield Fire Department, Hixton Fire Department, Lincoln Fire Department, Melrose Fire Department, Merrillan Fire Department, Osseo Fire Department, Pigeon Falls Fire Department, Pray Department of Natural Resources, Taylor Fire Department, and Tomah Department of Natural Resources.]
